We need to prove the theorem `as_extended_spec` which specifies the behavior of the `as_extended` function for `CompletedPoint` on the elliptic curve. The function converts a point from completed coordinates (ℙ¹ × ℙ¹) to extended twisted Edwards coordinates (ℙ³).

